{"tid":1973412,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"應否抽公屋 還是儲首期?","createTime":"2020-04-15T07:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T04:15:59.000Z","uid":48352,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd1958a349f16b0d0317016ecf1bdff97d828b1","tid":1973412,"uid":48352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:31:05.000Z","msg":"最近有個煩惱 諗緊第時結婚住屋問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先講下背景 同屋企人住緊公屋 (買左) 屋企人有一間屯門既細單位收緊租 佢地就黎退休諗住用黎租金養老<br />\n咁我之前同家姐一齊抽左公屋 佢就黎結婚所以俾佢住 諗落都覺得自己偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方案: <br />\n1.結左婚先再拆名出黎排公屋 住屋企人個單位俾返三分二租佢地<br />\n2.照結婚 出去租其他單位住<br />\n3.唔結婚住 拖返幾年儲到首期先(唔知儲幾耐先夠)"},{"pid":"c6348816b1cda9483eaa4acd37cae5f7bbd006cb","tid":1973412,"uid":103248,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:35:20.000Z","msg":"你確定你結左婚2個人既收入仲可以排到公屋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f403d20b532030e0bb49a38e2224eaef361126cf","tid":1973412,"uid":48352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6348816b1cda9483eaa4acd37cae5f7bbd006cb","tid":1973412,"uid":103248,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:35:20.000Z","msg":"你確定你結左婚2個人既收入仲可以排到公屋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:38:04.000Z","msg":"我諗要有一方現金出糧同要見官前辭職<br />\n定係而家個制度已經係你排緊個時超左都唔排得?"},{"pid":"e1701cc37d6a4f63ce494ecb80b7a4e45c3ae1e9","tid":1973412,"uid":48286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:40:23.000Z","msg":"租老母個單位<br />\n佢地百年歸老後間屋歸你<br />\n如果家姐反對<br />\n就同佢調轉，佢交間公屋你地住，佢租老母間屋"},{"pid":"915512ae0fea77b925772ca1723268f711447267","tid":1973412,"uid":103248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f403d20b532030e0bb49a38e2224eaef361126cf","tid":1973412,"uid":48352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6348816b1cda9483eaa4acd37cae5f7bbd006cb","tid":1973412,"uid":103248,"l